3#ifndef __NVKM_MMU_PRIV_H__
4#define __NVKM_MMU_PRIV_H__
5#define nvkm_mmu(p) container_of((p), struct nvkm_mmu, subdev)
6#include <subdev/mmu.h>
7
8void nvkm_mmu_ctor(const struct nvkm_mmu_func *, struct nvkm_device *,
9 int index, struct nvkm_mmu *);
10int nvkm_mmu_new_(const struct nvkm_mmu_func *, struct nvkm_device *,
11 int index, struct nvkm_mmu **);
12
13struct nvkm_mmu_func {
14 void *(*dtor)(struct nvkm_mmu *);
15 int (*oneinit)(struct nvkm_mmu *);
16 void (*init)(struct nvkm_mmu *);
17
18 u64 limit;
19 u8 dma_bits;
20 u32 pgt_bits;
21 u8 spg_shift;
22 u8 lpg_shift;
23
24 int (*create)(struct nvkm_mmu *, u64 offset, u64 length, u64 mm_offset,
25 struct lock_class_key *, struct nvkm_vm **);
26
27 void (*map_pgt)(struct nvkm_gpuobj *pgd, u32 pde,
28 struct nvkm_memory *pgt[2]);
29 void (*map)(struct nvkm_vma *, struct nvkm_memory *,
30 struct nvkm_mem *, u32 pte, u32 cnt,
31 u64 phys, u64 delta);
32 void (*map_sg)(struct nvkm_vma *, struct nvkm_memory *,
33 struct nvkm_mem *, u32 pte, u32 cnt, dma_addr_t *);
34 void (*unmap)(struct nvkm_vma *, struct nvkm_memory *pgt,
35 u32 pte, u32 cnt);
36 void (*flush)(struct nvkm_vm *);
37};
38
39int nvkm_vm_create(struct nvkm_mmu *, u64, u64, u64, u32,
40 struct lock_class_key *, struct nvkm_vm **);
41#endif
